'''Ferson''' was a [[Gender/Legends|male]] member of [[Talon Karrde]]'s [[Car'das/Legends|organization]]. In [[26 ABY/Legends|26 ABY]], he went to [[Yavin 4/Legends|Yavin 4]] with Karrde, [[Shada D'ukal]], and [[Halm (Human)|Halm]] to protect the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] students.

